<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>We do not promise outcomes. We build them — systematically, from Year 1.</h1>
    <p>BridgeDegree is not a series of workshops. It is career infrastructure — a structured system that operates alongside your university education and produces verified, documented proof of your capability at every stage.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 16px; font-weight: 600;">Here is exactly how it works.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>From 100 Level to your first global career — a structured path.</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">The student journey, year by year</p>
    <div class="journey-timeline">
      <div class="journey-item">
        <h3>100 Level — Enrolment & Foundation</h3>
        <p>You join BridgeDegree and complete your Career Assessment. Based on your assessment, you are matched to your programme mentor. Your Career Passport is created.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="journey-item">
        <h3>200 Level — First Internship Placement</h3>
        <p>Your first structured internship begins. BridgeDegree matches you to a vetted corporate partner. Your performance is tracked and at the end, your supervisor completes a formal performance review that is authenticated and added to your Career Passport.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="journey-item">
        <h3>300–400 Level — International Placements & Research Alignment</h3>
        <p>You progress to higher-complexity placements. Your final-year project brief is aligned to a real industry problem. BridgeDegree connects you with a co-author and begins the editorial preparation process for publication submission.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="journey-item">
        <h3>Final Year — Publication Submission & Career Passport Completion</h3>
        <p>Your co-authored research paper is submitted to an approved, indexed, peer-reviewed journal. Your Career Passport is complete — aggregating 2+ years of verified experience, publication records, and mentor endorsements.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="journey-item">
        <h3>Post-Graduation & NYSC — BridgeDegree After</h3>
        <p>For NYSC corps members, BridgeDegree After activates a dedicated career placement module. For students pursuing international opportunities, the Global Mobility Framework delivers visa application guidance and post-NYSC migration planning.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section" style="background: var(--surface-2);">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>The three engines — in detail</h2>
    <div class="engine-detail">
      <h3>Engine 1: Work Experience Engine</h3>
      <p>The Work Experience Engine begins at 200 Level and runs continuously until graduation. It includes structured internships with vetted partners, mandatory mentor assignment, BridgeDegree's performance evaluation framework, and blockchain-authenticated verification of every placement.</p>
      <p><strong>What you graduate with:</strong> 2+ years of verified, documented, employer-legible work experience.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="engine-detail">
      <h3>Engine 2: Publication Pipeline</h3>
      <p>Your final-year project is aligned to a real industry brief, co-authored with your supervisor and/or an industry expert, and submitted to journals on BridgeDegree's approved whitelist — vetted against Scopus, Web of Science, and DOAJ.</p>
      <p><strong>Quality standard:</strong> BridgeDegree maintains a strict journal whitelist. We never submit to predatory publishers.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="engine-detail">
      <h3>Engine 3: Global Mobility Framework</h3>
      <p>The Global Mobility Framework is the aspirational tier — available as an add-on. It includes scholarship research and application strategy, SOP development, referee selection, international CV development and ATS calibration, LinkedIn optimisation, and post-graduation migration support.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>The Career Passport — your crown asset</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Everything you produce through BridgeDegree is aggregated into a single document: your Career Passport.</p>
    <div class="passport-box">
      <h3>The Career Passport is:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Blockchain-credentialed</strong> — tamper-proof, permanently recorded, and independently verifiable</li>
        <li><strong>Globally legible</strong> — structured for international employer standards</li>
        <li><strong>Instantly verifiable</strong> — any employer anywhere can verify your credentials in seconds</li>
        <li><strong>Permanently yours</strong> — your Career Passport belongs to you</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section" style="background: var(--surface-2);">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Publication quality & journal standards</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Our journal standards:</p>
    <ul class="standards-list">
      <li>All approved journals are indexed in Scopus, Web of Science, or DOAJ</li>
      <li>A BridgeDegree journal whitelist is published on the website and updated annually</li>
      <li>No submissions are made to any journal not on the whitelist</li>
      <li>BridgeDegree provides an editorial review before any submission</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top: 24px;"><a href="/students" class="btn-primary">Start your application <i data-lucide="arrow-right"></i></a></p>
